{
  "texts": [
    "According to the underlying systems, these techniques can be categorized into radar-centric, communication-centric, and joint design.",
    "We first review the radar-centric ISAC techniques, including radar-centric waveform design and receive signal processing.",
    "Then, we review the communication-centric ISAC techniques, including communication-centric waveform design and estimation of sensor parameters.",
    "Finally, we review the joint design ISAC techniques from the perspective of waveform design, beamforming design, and transceiver design.",
    "Radar-centric ISAC techniquesIn radar-centric ISAC systems, communication symbols are embedded in the radar waveform using various signaling strategies."
  ]
}